OL,3,CCouncil approves closure of four adult
OL,4,Cday centres despite opposition
OL,6,FThe closures follow the "Your Day,
OL,7,FYour Say" consultation, which ran from
OL,8,FMay to July 2024, during which many
OL,9,Fcarers and advocates for people with
OL,10,Flearning disabilities and autism
OL,11,Fvoiced concerns about the impact on
OL,12,Fvulnerable individuals who rely on
OL,13,Fthese centres for stability, social
OL,14,Finteraction, and support.
OL,16,FMore than 69% of respondents,
OL,17,Fincluding carers and citizens,
OL,18,Fstrongly disagreed with the proposals.
OL,20,FSome carers spoke about the effects
OL,21,Fthe closures would have.
