OL,3,CCouncil approves closure of four adult
OL,4,Cday centres despite opposition
OL,6,F"My brother has attended Harborne for
OL,7,Fover 20 years. Moving him would cause
OL,8,Fgreat distress," said one carer,
OL,9,Fechoing the worries of many about the
OL,10,Femotional and mental toll the closures
OL,11,Fwill have on long-term service users.
OL,13,FAnother carer added, "These centres
OL,14,Fprovide vital respite care for people
OL,15,Flike myself. Without them, I don't
OL,16,Fknow how we'll manage."
