OL,3,CCouncil approves closure of four adult
OL,4,Cday centres despite opposition
OL,6,FA major issue raised by critics is the
OL,7,Fincreased travel times for citizens,
OL,8,Fparticularly those in south
OL,9,FBirmingham, who could face up to an
OL,10,Fadditional hour's journey each way to
OL,11,Fthe remaining centres.
OL,13,F"The longer travel will be too much
OL,14,Ffor my father, who is already frail,"
OL,15,Fone resident shared.
OL,17,FStaff shortages have exacerbated
OL,18,Fconcerns, with over 70 vacancies,
OL,19,Fincluding key driver positions,
OL,20,Ffurther complicating transport
OL,21,Farrangements.
