OL,3,CCouncil approves closure of four adult
OL,4,Cday centres despite opposition
OL,6,FLocal groups, such as the Central
OL,7,FEngland Law Centre, have questioned
OL,8,Fthe data underpinning the closures,
OL,9,Farguing that the council failed to
OL,10,Ffully consider the ongoing impact of
OL,11,Fthe Covid pandemic on attendance
OL,12,Ffigures.
OL,14,FOne representative said: "The pandemic
OL,15,Fdrastically changed how people
OL,16,Faccessed services, and this decision
OL,17,Ffeels rushed without taking that
OL,18,Freality into account."
