OL,3,CCouncil approves closure of four adult
OL,4,Cday centres despite opposition
OL,6,FDespite the criticism, the council has
OL,7,Fdefended its analysis, citing the need
OL,8,Ffor financial sustainability.
OL,10,FIt has also stated no jobs will be
OL,11,Flost as a result of the closures, and
OL,12,Fthat remaining centres will benefit
OL,13,Ffrom improved services.
OL,15,FIn response to the concerns, the
OL,16,Fcouncil has pledged comprehensive
OL,17,Fsupport during the transition period.
