OL,3,CCouncil approves closure of four adult
OL,4,Cday centres despite opposition
OL,6,FThis includes ensuring familiar staff
OL,7,Fwill assist with relocations and
OL,8,Foffering options such as external Day
OL,9,FOpportunity Services and Direct
OL,10,FPayments.
OL,12,FWhile the council stresses that these
OL,13,Fchanges are necessary for long-term
OL,14,Fsustainability, the closures have left
OL,15,Fmany citizens and carers feeling
OL,16,Fanxious about the future, with
OL,17,Fwidespread concern that the decision
OL,18,Fwill disrupt lives and reduce access
OL,19,Fto essential care services.
